## This action will scale glyphs that have been 
## transferred from a 2048 em unit font to a
## 1000 em unit font.
##-----------------------------------------------------
##
set F1 aw            
set F2 lsb  
set F3 [100*1000/2048]
origin 0 0
stretch F3 F3
set lsb [F2*1000/2048]
set aw [F1*1000/2048]
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
